{
  "stem": "20084.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we had to go to the houses, and scrub the floors, and clean everything, and sweep just streets, and all kinds of manual-- manual labor, unloading-- unloading coal from the railroad, and-- and potatoes, whatever-- whatever it was, manual labor.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we were lucky if I got a bowl of soup for the work.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[SIGHS] And [SIGHS] this was the beginning.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then was we had to register.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They form a-- they issue another proclamation that all the Jews have to move into a certain section of Cracow.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "This is [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And you can bring only so much with you, what you can carry and whatever.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And you have to leave everything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I lived already in that place where they were forming the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I didn't have to move.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were already in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we-- we formed-- what do you call it?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Oh, then-- then we had to start lining up, lining up for bread, to get a loaf of bread.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I remember on one of those outings standing up all night for a piece of-- the whole family was lining up because just in case they run short of bread, or one of us will be able to get a bread.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we all line up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- I remember on one of those outings, my mother got bitten by the German dog.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He just-- just got bitten.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I don't remember even if we got a bread that time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we all were lining up all night to get a bread.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's what started a lot of-- a lot of trouble, a lot of trouble, a lot of trouble for us. for us.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
